review: It's Fridays. Close to school, quick service and tasty food. Got the job done, but wouldn't go out of my way to come back.

This was not gourmet dining but the food was tasty and nicely prepared!  The manager was vigilant about keeping customers happy.  I just ate there a week ago and was shocked to see it had closed.  I  also recenly learned the Friday's in Phoenix as well as Surprise has closed.  I will miss the Glendale Friday's.
